### API Biblioteca Digital — REST Client Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = PEGA_TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Auth

### Registrar usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "María García",
  "email": "maria@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "MiPassword123!"
}

###

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "MiPassword123!"
}

###

### Login Admin (del seed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@biblioteca.com",
  "password": "Admin1234!"
}

###

### Login Bibliotecario (del seed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "librarian@biblioteca.com",
  "password": "Librarian1234!"
}

###

### Obtener mi perfil
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Libros

###

### Listar libros (público)
GET {{baseUrl}}/books

###

### Listar libros con filtros
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?genre=Fantasía&available=true&page=1&limit=5

###

### Obtener libro por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/1

###

### Crear libro (requiere LIBRARIAN o ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isbn": "978-84-376-0494-7",
  "title": "Don Quijote de la Mancha",
  "author": "Miguel de Cervantes",
  "genre": "Clásico",
  "description": "La obra más importante de la literatura española.",
  "publishedYear": 1605,
  "copies": 4
}

###

### Actualizar libro (requiere LIBRARIAN o ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/books/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Don Quijote de la Mancha (Edición actualizada)",
  "copies": 6
}

###

### Eliminar libro (requiere ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/books/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Préstamos

###

### Solicitar préstamo
POST {{baseUrl}}/loans
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "bookId": 1
}

###

### Mis préstamos
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Todos los préstamos (LIBRARIAN/ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Todos los préstamos con filtro de estado
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans/all?status=ACTIVE&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Devolver libro
PUT {{baseUrl}}/loans/1/return
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reseñas

###

### Reseñas de un libro (público)
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/1/reviews

###

### Crear reseña (solo si has devuelto el libro)
POST {{baseUrl}}/books/1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excelente libro, muy recomendable."
}

###

### Eliminar reseña
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reviews/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Estadísticas

###

### Estadísticas generales (LIBRARIAN/ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Marcar préstamos vencidos y obtener lista (LIBRARIAN/ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/stats/overdue
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Health

###

### Health check (con ping a BD)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

###

### Readiness probe
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ready
